{
  "chapter": 8,
  "chapter_summary": "第八章\"九指擒龙\"中，广西五虎受屈寒山蒙蔽，误以为萧秋水等人为恶人，虽经唐方与文鬓霜竭力辩白，仍不获信任而离去。萧秋水等八人陷入绝境，被屈寒山及六大人魔团团围困。关键时刻，江易海突然反戈，以九指擒龙扣住屈寒山死穴，揭露其真实身份为六扇门三大至尊之一的\"九指神捕\"胡十四。胡十四卧底权力帮七年，此刻为救萧秋水等人毅然暴露身份，催促众人先行撤离。然而屈寒山以内力骤然爆发挣脱束缚，一剑将胡十四拦腰斩杀。萧秋水等人仓皇逃至古严关，却发现余哭余已在沿途布下剧毒，无辜樵夫触碰死者尸身即中毒身亡。余哭余三弟子余笑不、余不笑、余我吾现身拦截，以暗器投毒袭击萧秋水，萧秋水中毒倒下，生死未卜，本章在悬念中结束。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_dao_hu_fu",
      "speaker_name": "金刀胡福",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "listener_name": "屈寒山",
      "text": "这的确是一场误会……我们本来也觉得以康先生、彭兄之侠名，怎会作出这等事情……幸而屈大侠及时赶到，才化解这……这一场误会。要请大家海涵，见谅。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_chu_yu",
      "speaker_name": "康出渔",
      "listener": "char_guang_xi_wu_hu",
      "listener_name": "广西五虎",
      "text": "见谅则不敢当，不过五位他日要行侠，要仗义，还是要问清楚才出手较好！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hei",
      "speaker_name": "李黑",
      "listener": "char_kang_chu_yu",
      "listener_name": "康出渔",
      "text": "我们两广十虎，天不怕、地不怕，服的只有两人，在广东，是梁斗梁大侠，在广西，是屈大侠，倒不是你康老先生，康先生说这话，未免太托大了一些吧！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_guang_xi_wu_hu",
      "listener_name": "广西五虎",
      "text": "总之是一场误会……我以'屈寒山'三个字作保证，这些人狐群狗党，不值五位匡护……至于冲突，兹代表康先生等位向诸位道歉。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_lin_hong_hua",
      "speaker_name": "少林洪华",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "listener_name": "屈寒山",
      "text": "有屈大侠出面，我们自是心服口服。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_bei_lao_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "躬背劳九",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "listener_name": "屈寒山",
      "text": "有屈大侠开了声，我们就此不管！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_guang_xi_wu_hu",
      "listener_name": "广西五虎",
      "text": "几位如此给屈某薄面，不知可否至寒舍小酌几杯？能否赏光？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hei",
      "speaker_name": "李黑",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "listener_name": "屈寒山",
      "text": "恐怕没有心情了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_dao_hu_fu",
      "speaker_name": "金刀胡福",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "listener_name": "屈寒山",
      "text": "这几天梁斗梁大侠要来，兄弟等还要张罗接待，届时梁大侠来了，才一齐去拜会屈大侠，如此可好？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_jin_dao_hu_fu",
      "listener_name": "金刀胡福",
      "text": "梁大侠吗？我已经好久没见过他了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_guang_xi_wu_hu",
      "listener_name": "广西五虎",
      "text": "你们竟相信这人的话？！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hei",
      "speaker_name": "李黑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "listener_name": "萧秋水",
      "text": "屈大侠是广西群龙之首，自是不会骗人！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_fang",
      "speaker_name": "唐方",
      "listener": "char_guang_xi_wu_hu",
      "listener_name": "广西五虎",
      "text": "我是唐方，我的哥哥唐大，就是死在这姓康的手上。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_fang",
      "speaker_name": "唐方",
      "listener": "char_guang_xi_wu_hu",
      "listener_name": "广西五虎",
      "text": "他的确是文老前辈，其他三绝一君，都死于这屈寒山手下！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_dao_hu_fu",
      "speaker_name": "金刀胡福",
      "listener": "char_tang_fang",
      "listener_name": "唐方",
      "text": "姑娘救胡某一命，胡某自是感激；只是姑娘说唐大先生已遭毒手，在下却在十日前，还与唐大先生会面，姑娘说的未免太……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "至于四绝一君，与我相交十数年，江湖宵小也不知剪除多少了，我会杀他们？！哈！哈哈哈……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_za_he_shi_yue",
      "speaker_name": "杂鹤施月",
      "listener": "char_tang_fang",
      "listener_name": "唐方",
      "text": "不是我们不信任你们，而是你们说的话，令人无法信任。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_guang_xi_wu_hu",
      "listener_name": "广西五虎",
      "text": "你们走吧，我们不怨你们。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "listener_name": "萧秋水等人",
      "text": "现在都好了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_jing_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "马竟终",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "listener_name": "屈寒山",
      "text": "什么都好了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "listener_name": "萧秋水等人",
      "text": "应该准备好了吧？要自刎呢？还是要我们来动手？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "listener_name": "萧秋水等人",
      "text": "要杀你们，易如反掌。前面还有汉四海在等你们，后面也有余哭余在追。你们，已无一线生机。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "listener_name": "萧秋水等人",
      "text": "既然你们不肯自杀，我们只好动手了。你们已知道我们那么多秘密，我们自然没有法子让你们再活下去。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "listener_name": "屈寒山",
      "text": "你要杀就杀，要我们束手待毙，绝不可能！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "listener_name": "萧秋水",
      "text": "好！我就先杀你！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yi_hai",
      "speaker_name": "江易海",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "listener_name": "屈寒山",
      "text": "请剑王让我先行出手。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yi_hai",
      "listener_name": "江易海",
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yi_hai",
      "listener_name": "江易海",
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yi_hai",
      "speaker_name": "江易海",
      "listener": "char_kang_chu_yu",
      "listener_name": "康出渔等人",
      "text": "你们想要剑王的命，最好先住手。要帮主不责你们之失职，就得听我的，要是帮主怪罪，你们在这儿赔了个'剑王'，嘿嘿，你们当知惩罚如何了！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yi_hai",
      "listener_name": "江易海",
      "text": "你究竟是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yi_hai",
      "speaker_name": "江易海",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "listener_name": "萧秋水",
      "text": "我是'五湖拿四海'江易海。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yi_hai",
      "listener_name": "江易海",
      "text": "难怪陕北道上，你曾拿住了我，却没有杀我，你就是'九指神捕'胡十四！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yi_hai",
      "speaker_name": "江易海（胡十四）",
      "listener": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "listener_name": "左丘超然",
      "text": "要不是你师叔，还会给你一个臭屁就臭走？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yi_hai",
      "speaker_name": "胡十四",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "listener_name": "萧秋水等人",
      "text": "因为我九只手指，跟别人都不一样，所以柳大总管还是怀疑我，始终没让我接近李沉舟，也没让我当上'九天十地，十九人魔'其中之一，所以我花了七年，还是掘不着'权力帮'的根。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yi_hai",
      "speaker_name": "胡十四",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "listener_name": "萧秋水等人",
      "text": "而今我已忍无可忍，不能让你们白白送死，所以这下出手，杀一个李沉舟爱将屈剑王也好！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_chu_yu",
      "speaker_name": "康出渔",
      "listener": "char_hu_shi_si",
      "listener_name": "胡十四",
      "text": "你是胡十四？！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_shi_si",
      "speaker_name": "胡十四",
      "listener": "char_kang_chu_yu",
      "listener_name": "康出渔",
      "text": "你的底子，都落到我手里，你很愤怒，是不是？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_chu_yu",
      "speaker_name": "康出渔",
      "listener": "char_hu_shi_si",
      "listener_name": "胡十四",
      "text": "为着权力帮，我不能让你活回去！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_shi_si",
      "speaker_name": "胡十四",
      "listener": "char_kang_chu_yu",
      "listener_name": "康出渔",
      "text": "不过只要你再走前一步，我就杀了屈剑王！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_shi_si",
      "speaker_name": "胡十四",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "listener_name": "萧秋水等人",
      "text": "你们先走，这儿让我来断后。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": "char_hu_shi_si",
      "listener_name": "胡十四",
      "text": "胡师叔！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_shi_si",
      "speaker_name": "胡十四",
      "listener": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "listener_name": "左丘超然",
      "text": "你要是认我是师叔，那就赶快给我走！带你那班朋友立刻走！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_shi_si",
      "speaker_name": "胡十四",
      "listener": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "listener_name": "左丘超然",
      "text": "并且回去告诉你师父，这个时候不是归隐可以躲得开的，你不先找他，他会毁了整个江湖，然后就是你！",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_shi_si",
      "speaker_name": "胡十四",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "listener_name": "萧秋水",
      "text": "萧秋水，你们快走，别忘了浣花剑派，武林同道命脉，都系在你们所要传达的讯息上！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_hu_shi_si",
      "listener_name": "胡十四",
      "text": "胡前辈你……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_shi_si",
      "speaker_name": "胡十四",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "listener_name": "萧秋水",
      "text": "我手上还有这位'剑王'，他们还不敢对我怎样，而且，我一个人也较容易脱身得多，你们跟着我反而累事。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_shi_si",
      "speaker_name": "胡十四",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "listener_name": "萧秋水",
      "text": "还不快走！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_shi_si",
      "speaker_name": "胡十四",
      "listener": "char_kang_chu_yu",
      "listener_name": "康出渔等人",
      "text": "现在我也想走了，你们能不能提供我个好办法？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_chu_yu",
      "speaker_name": "康出渔",
      "listener": "char_hu_shi_si",
      "listener_name": "胡十四",
      "text": "你先放了剑王，我以名誉保证，让你活出广西。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_shi_si",
      "speaker_name": "胡十四",
      "listener": "char_kang_chu_yu",
      "listener_name": "康出渔",
      "text": "你的名誉担保，哈……敢情是屈寒山对广西五虎的保证一样吧？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 317
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_shi_si",
      "speaker_name": "胡十四",
      "listener": "char_kang_chu_yu",
      "listener_name": "康出渔",
      "text": "我放了屈寒山，不但活不出广西，连万里桥也活不过了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_qian_bian",
      "speaker_name": "柳千变",
      "listener": "char_hu_shi_si",
      "listener_name": "胡十四",
      "text": "那你究竟想怎样？！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_shi_si",
      "speaker_name": "胡十四",
      "listener": "char_liu_qian_bian",
      "listener_name": "柳千变",
      "text": "我想还是——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_kang_chu_yu",
      "listener_name": "康出渔等人",
      "text": "快追！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "樵夫甲",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": "樵夫乙",
      "text": "听说四川武林中出了一件惨案，死了很多会打架的人，你知也不知？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "樵夫乙",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": "樵夫甲",
      "text": "哦！是那个叫什么剑派的吗？好像给人攻破了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "樵夫甲",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": "樵夫乙",
      "text": "可不是吗？跟权力帮作对，有死无生咯！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "樵夫乙",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": "樵夫甲",
      "text": "晤怪之得啦，原来拒地与权力帮作对，想唔死都几难咯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_fang",
      "speaker_name": "唐方",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "listener_name": "萧秋水等人",
      "text": "是被人毒死的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_jing_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "马竟终",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "都是些普通的樵子。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_shan_yi",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳珊一",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "一定是瘟疫人魔余哭余，早布下了毒，却误毒死几个不相干的人！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "樵夫丙",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "那个不是鲁阿根吗？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "樵夫丁",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "他怎么也会在那里？谁干的……阴功！阿弟也在那边！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "樵夫丁",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "阿弟，阿弟，你怎样了？",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_bin_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "文鬓霜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "listener_name": "萧秋水、左丘超然",
      "text": "等一等！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_bin_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "文鬓霜",
      "listener": null,
      "listener_name": null,
      "text": "下来！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_xiao_bu",
      "speaker_name": "余笑不",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "listener_name": "萧秋水等人",
      "text": "我叫余笑不，他叫余不笑，还有一个，就叫余我吾。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "余不笑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "listener_name": "萧秋水等人",
      "text": "我们都是余哭余的弟子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 449,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wo_wu",
      "speaker_name": "余我吾",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "listener_name": "萧秋水等人",
      "text": "我们本来要毒死你们，却毒死了别人，这样也好，死越多人，越好！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 455
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_xiao_bu",
      "speaker_name": "余笑不",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "listener_name": "萧秋水等人",
      "text": "我师父就要来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 461,
      "line_end": 463
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "余不笑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "listener_name": "萧秋水等人",
      "text": "我们要在师父未来前解决你们。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 465,
      "line_end": 467
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wo_wu",
      "speaker_name": "余我吾",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "listener_name": "萧秋水等人",
      "text": "你们谁要先来送死？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 469,
      "line_end": 471
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_yu_xiao_bu",
      "listener_name": "余笑不等人",
      "text": "你们残杀无辜，我先来领教！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 473,
      "line_end": 475
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_yu_xiao_bu",
      "listener_name": "余笑不等人",
      "text": "凭这些小道技俩也把我……",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 479,
      "line_end": 479
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "speaker_name": "铁星月",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "listener_name": "萧秋水",
      "text": "萧老大——！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 481,
      "line_end": 483
    },
    {
